  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large pot over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add the sliced onions and sauté until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and ginger, cooking for another minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the shiitake and button mushrooms, browning them on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Mix in the tomato paste and soy sauce, coating the mushrooms evenly.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth, stirring to combine, then add the bay leaf and turmeric.",
    "Bring the mixture to a gentle boil, reduce heat to low, and simmer uncovered for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the bay leaf, season with salt and pepper to taste, and serve hot over steamed rice or noodles."
